Key West is a city and an island of the same name near the southernmost tip of the Florida Keys and the Continental US. It is the county seat of Monroe County, Florida, United States. It is at 24°33′N 81°46′W and is about south-southwest of Miami and about north-northeast of Havana in Cuba. == References == ==Other websites== * Official City Website * Chamber of Commerce Website * Monroe County School District Key West Public Schools * Oldest Hotel in Key West * Key West Art Galleries * A photographic tour of Key West * Getting to Key West, the road down US1 * Sanborn Insurance Historical Maps of Key West Category:Cities in Florida Category:Florida Keys Category:County seats in Florida
